## Ingredients

- Yukon gold potatoes
- Cream Cheese
- Butter
- Salt
- Pepper

## Instructions

1. Skin and quarter potatoes
2. Boil potatoes for 20-25 minutes
3. Drain
4. Lightly mash
5. Put in butter and cream cheese and salt
6. Mash more
7. Taste test, add more butter, cream cheese, or salt to taste

